{"tid":2077563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憲法教授梁美芬：同志集會意淫、淫褻、有傷風化","createTime":"2020-06-24T11:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T11:59:25.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4b065326fe33d94d16aedef71586fd88233d09","tid":2077563,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">憲法教授梁美芬的同路人= 趙佩玉</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前北區區議會通過成為今年同志遊行的支持機構。反同團體「愛家工程」今日到政府總部外示威，並向經民聯梁美芬遞信，反對區議會支持同志遊行，並<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">促請政府監管「有傷風化」及「淫褻性」的同志遊行集會</span></strong>。全港逾百名區議員發聲明反擊，表明支持同志平權，並反對梁美芬干預北區區議會。<br />\n<br />\n團體高舉標語，除了反對區議會「濫用公帑」推廣同志遊行之外，亦批評香港電台去年曾直播同志遊行，並<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>指同志是「以意淫及裸露行為示眾」</strong></span>等。曾於 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2018 年以「上帝叫我參選」、「天父話我會贏」</span></strong>為由參加新東立法會補選的趙佩玉，今日亦有參與遞信。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/lgbtq/%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E8%81%AF%E5%8F%8D%E5%90%8C%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94-%E6%96%A5%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%91%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E7%99%BC%E6%92%90%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Flgbtq%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258A%25AC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594-%25E6%2596%25A5%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2591%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BF%2597%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2592%2590%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%2581%25B2%2